What is Amazon Renewed?

Amazon Renewed is your trusted destination for products that are inspected, tested, and refurbished as necessary to be fully functional.

Quality you can afford

Amazon Renewed products offer an affordable option so you can save on the brands you love.

Products you can trust

All products have been professionally inspected, tested, cleaned, and refurbished as necessary by Amazon-qualified suppliers. Products are not certified by Apple.

Purchases with an impact

Your Amazon Renewed purchase extends the lifetime of this product and reduces electronic waste.

Trusted coverage

Your purchase is eligible for Amazon Renewed coverage in conjunction with Amazon's Return Policy and the A-to-z Guarantee.

What should I expect to receive with my Amazon Renewed purchase?

All Amazon Renewed purchases will come with accessories equivalent to those that shipped in the box when new. These items may not be original but will be compatible and fully functional. Amazon Renewed products will be packaged in either original packaging or in a new and clean cardboard box.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Learn more how customers reviews work on Amazon

    Customers say

    Customers find the iPhone 15 Pro Max to be in mint condition, looking exactly like new, and worth the price tag. The phone's battery health receives mixed feedback, with some reporting 98% capacity while others get less than 90%. The scratch resistance receives mixed feedback, with some reporting no damage while others mention scratches on the screen.

      I live in Colombia and received the phone through a freight forwarder. Unfortunately, the device arrived with several issues: the battery overheats and drains very quickly, and both the screen and the battery are not genuine. The main camera lens is scratched, causing blurry focus and photo defects, and there was also cosmetic wear not mentioned in the listing.

      Ive previously purchased refurbished Apple products in excellent conditionincluding Apple Watches and MacBooksand this is the first time Ive had an experience like this. For context, I purchased this phone listed as excellent condition.

      I contacted the seller and, after seeing some positive reviews, suggested a replacement. However, they said they had no stock available. They offered $25 to keep the phone or a refund, which doesnt even come close to covering all these defects. They also stated that if I was outside the U.S., they wouldnt cover return shippingfortunately, my freight forwarding service allows returns, but not all do.

      Luckily, I still had my iPhone 13, which allowed me to wait for the refund process without being left without a phone.

      Since a replacement isnt possible, returning the device for a full refund is the only solution
